OSM Shuya

Interactive map of Shuya-city based on OpenStreetMap and OpenLayers.


Deployment
-----------
# clone repository
git clone git://github.com/scalm/OSM-Shuya.git
cd OSM-Shuya
# fetch and configure dependencies
./configure.sh

Development
-----------
Config ./src/www as web root directory for site.

# configure site (may differ)
# ln -s ./src/www /var/www/site

Production
---------
# copying files
./configure.sh dist

# configure site (may differ)
# mkdir -p /var/www/site
# cp -R ./dist/www /var/www/site

# remove temporary files
# rm -rf ./dist

